{"tid":905303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人好無恥 【河南採砂摧殘河流】","createTime":"2018-11-17T04:25:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T04:25:54.000Z","uid":74778,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4e67d4a40063d757e4aeea8c8008e07b726a76da","tid":905303,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:25:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1941086206035856/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F1941086206035856%2F&d=s3MI7VAOkm5bhBhmo8PddDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=ff7474df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1941086206035856/</a><br />\n<br />\n【河南採砂摧殘河流】<br />\n【因地方政府為疏理河道拍賣河砂】<br />\n<br />\n河南鲁山的沙河和蕩澤河蘊含豐富砂石資源，是一級水源保護地，但因為多年來被過度採砂，被摧殘得「不成河形」。但其實政府多年前已經加強河道管理，但非法採砂仍禁之不絕。<br />\n<br />\n原來當地政府開展一項「清障疏浚」治理工程，把河道中的砂石拍賣給七家企業，希望企業運走砂石疏通河道的同時，政府又可從中獲利，一舉兩得。但砂石還是採到越界，連村民的耕地都照挖，中央環保督察組點名批評魯山縣政府假以「清障疏浚」之名開發河砂，下令禁止當地任何砂石的開採、運輸和銷售行為。<br />\n<br />\n只不過到了晚上河邊就有多輛貨車排長龍，監察人員更聲稱巡查時從未發現有人採砂，值班紀錄竟然都是空白一片。媒體揭發事件，當地政府便立案查處，並已經鎖定疑犯。<br />\n<br />\n#河南<br />\n#採砂<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"fce66a07334764460268f0ea1fbb56e2b11357d6","tid":905303,"uid":65984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:45:18.000Z","msg":"賣完河砂然後修復, GDP gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075582b3cfc4a4ade1a8b784e7671664cbb7d332","tid":905303,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fce66a07334764460268f0ea1fbb56e2b11357d6","tid":905303,"uid":65984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:45:18.000Z","msg":"賣完河砂然後修復, GDP gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:20:38.000Z","msg":"真係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dca655bbaf485ad10a914f62c24f15ca87fa0a3","tid":905303,"uid":4575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:21:54.000Z","msg":"唔係邊夠砂起人工島"},{"pid":"4978d205107318dbe7c0add75658f2e95af636fc","tid":905303,"uid":56940,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:25:19.000Z","msg":"同中國人講保育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f36ef4cae56da7d2783a31c47b17d0fd7e70a5","tid":905303,"uid":18569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4978d205107318dbe7c0add75658f2e95af636fc","tid":905303,"uid":56940,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:25:19.000Z","msg":"同中國人講保育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天大笑話"},{"pid":"d43f27a2975a0ab526bc6511d6bb5fcd26d2b691","tid":905303,"uid":23833,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:29:22.000Z","msg":"無恥？我覺戇鳩姐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沙根本唔值錢<br />\n<br />\n知你香港填海升幾十倍"},{"pid":"66b5e0ba29d994a19f672d0e5819e5aa6e8d6873","tid":905303,"uid":159307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:33:51.000Z","msg":"支那搞爛自己地方值得支持"},{"pid":"21ac54885452a9bf8c51024d56bf97609f5116a0","tid":905303,"uid":173930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:36:38.000Z","msg":"賤種係無得教，只可以殺"},{"pid":"c93884689ad22391e9555d7abc693666e1cd879b","tid":905303,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21ac54885452a9bf8c51024d56bf97609f5116a0","tid":905303,"uid":173930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:36:38.000Z","msg":"賤種係無得教，只可以殺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T03:53:05.000Z","msg":"毛魔殺曬識字既人，奸到仆街既農民上曬位，做曬政治人物<br />\n<br />\n唔係無得教，無人教姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3175bc96c903dc180730534081a64761df32b499","tid":905303,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:19:26.00